## mise commands

| Command | What it does |
|---|---|
| `mise install` | Install pinned tools (node, pnpm, pulumi) |
| `mise run install` | Install infra dependencies |
| `mise run build` | Compile-check the program (`tsc --noEmit`) |
| `mise run test` | Unit tests (Pulumi mocks) |
| `mise run lint` | Biome check |
| `mise run dev` | `pulumi preview` for the current stack |
| `mise run infra:<task>` | Run an infra task directly (install/build/test/lint/typecheck/preview/up/destroy/refresh/policy) |

